--------------------      C-- Compiler  ------------------------------

This is a compiler of a C-like programming language ,so called "C--".
It is coded in C using the GNU Flex and Bison. 

------------------------Test Environment------------------------------
GNU Linux Release: Ubuntu 10.04, kernel version 2.6.35
GCC version 4.4.3
GNU Flex version 2.5.35
GNU Bison version 2.4.1 

------------------------Try it yourself ------------------------------
You can download the files, compile the code and run it on your Linux.
U just need to type in the "make" bash script.




